
ecf-0.0.4

* Mod: config dirs extension changed from ".d" to ".ecd" (z.B. desire.d -> desire.ecd) (for aestetic reason 8-)) 

ecf-0.0.3

* Mod: ecf-mule reorganised
* Add: precondition to desire. Now desire format is: (desire 'package "fname" "precond")

ecf-0.0.2

* Add: config dirs (z.B. desire.d) 
* Mod: prefix `rc' from config dirs removed
* Mod: host-wide configs in `/etc/ecf/'
* Mod: user configs in `~/.config/ecf/' (by `Desktop base directory spec' http://www.freedesktop.org/Standards/basedir-spec)
* Mod: cache files in `~/.cache/elisp/' (by `Desktop base directory spec' http://www.freedesktop.org/Standards/basedir-spec)
